retary of the treasury returned to georgia and was appointed judge of the northern circuit court in  which position he held until his death in oglethorpe county ga september   interment on his estate woodlawn near crawford oglethorpe county ga bibliographyamerican national biography dictionary of american biography green philip the life of william crawford chapel hill university of north carolina press  mooney chase william h crawford  lexington university press of kentucky